---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

// Usamos el Layout pero con noIndex={true} para que Google no indexe esta página de error.
---

<Layout
  noIndex={true}
>
  <section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-neutral-900 overflow-hidden px-4"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-5 pointer-events-none">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="600"
        height="600"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="0.5"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="text-white/20 rotate-12"
      >
        <path d="M10.585 10.587a2 2 0 0 0 2.829 2.828"></path>
        <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 7.071 2.929"></path>
        <path d="M22 12a10 10 0 0 1-2.929 7.071"></path>
        <path d="M12 22a10 10 0 0 1-7.071-2.929"></path>
        <path d="M2 12a10 10 0 0 1 2.929-7.071"></path>
        <path d="m2 2 20 20" class="text-winay/50" stroke-width="1"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1
        class="text-[120px] md:text-[180px] font-black leading-none bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-winay via-green-500 to-winay animate-pulse-slow filter drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)]"
      >
        404
      </h1>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-6">
        Esta página es como una estrategia sin embudo: <span class="text-winay">No lleva a ningún lado.</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Has llegado a un punto muerto digital. Esta URL no existe o ha cambiado. Afortunadamente, somos expertos en redirigir el tráfico hacia donde realmente importa: <strong class="text-white">las ventas</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-winay rounded-full hover:bg-green-600 shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-500/30"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
            </svg>
            Volver al camino del crecimiento
          </span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="/#cal"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-white/20 rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/40"
        >
          O agenda una asesoría directa
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Animación suave para el 404 */
  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; }
  }
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse-slow 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
</style>